results.name: Decimal expansion of Integrate[(1 - x)/((1 + x y) (Log[x y])^2),{y,0,1},{x,0,1}].
comment: Equals Integral_{u=0..1} (u - log(u) - 1)/((1 + u)*(log(u))^2). (Let u = x*y and v = y, and integrate w.r.t. v.) - _Petros Hadjicostas_, Jun 13 2020
